Gg_Power

Made by The Giblets of Jesus

This map was originally created for TopHATTWaffle's First annual mapping contest (I only came 5th :P) for creating a FY map in 24 hours. Since the contest I have been busy with exams amongst other things, so mapping hasn't really been a high priority (Hence the late release). The contest was quite fun and I advise anyone with an active interest in mapping to participate next year :).

THIS YEARS RESULTS!

A few Features of this map:

+High FPS +HDR +78 Spawns
